com.authlete.common.types

Class IdTokenClaims

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.common.types.IdTokenClaims

  • public class IdTokenClaims
extends Object
    Claims used within the ID Token for all OAuth 2.0 flows used by OpenID Connect.
    1. iss
    2. sub
    3. aud
    4. exp
    5. iat
    6. auth_time
    7. nonce
    8. acr
    9. amr
    10. azp
    Author:
    Takahiko Kawasaki
    See Also:
    OpenID Connect Core 1.0, 2. ID Token
